      </userestrict>
      <bioghist id="aspace_47877b8a972e2f66418819ce1a357c2d">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Joan Alzina, Catalan Republican and member of the Republican Army, served in the 24th Army Group, Group Logistics, 3rd Section. Alzina was held prisoner at Navalpino and later became a camp guard at Alcalá de Henares, a Madrid prison for Republican fighters.</p>  
      </bioghist>
